"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Bloom the most beautiful scenery with your heart. I believe that having a love can dispel the scorching sun; Believe that with a belief, you can build the most beautiful garden; I believe that if you stick to a stick, the backcountry can also bloom the most beautiful scenery.\\n\\nI am willing to inject a love into my heart, fill a belief and persistence, and bloom the most beautiful scenery of life!\\n\\nInject the water of faith into the garden of the soul and grow the brilliance of a garden.\\n\\nI don't know how one can hold on to the dawn in the endless night; I don't know how a person can hold his dream in the dense flowers and willows.\\n\\n我只知道，唯有信念，才能相信自己，筑起围墙，修复梦想！她做到了，因为她有信仰，她放弃了她数百万的家产；因为信仰，她勇敢地成为了村干部；大雨中为村民盖房，病中仍照料村民。\\n\\n她就是“最美村干部”段爱萍。\\n\\n一个村庄的梦想因她的信仰而萌芽和繁荣！在梦想的路上与信念携手同行，我的心是风景最美的花园！\\n\\n为灵魂之舟，满载货物坚守，更容易进入“桃花源”。\\n\\n谁不向往晴天无浪的美景呢？谁不期待日升落月落潮星辰的景色呢？人生需要一根棍子，才能创造出最美的风景。\\n\\n周有光懂得坚持，最终成为了人们称颂的“周氏百科全书”；乔布斯知道如何坚持，永不放弃，实现自己的苹果梦；教皇知道如何坚持下去。即使是最小的花朵也应该绽放并最终成为英国文学的大师。\\n\\n最美的风景往往在彼岸。只有懂得坚持的人，才能勇敢前行，闻到彼岸的一缕花香；将膝盖抱在沙滩上，欣赏最美的风景！\\n\\n“我来自该地区，去了天堂，并在途中经过了世界。\\n\\n“是的！作为生活的过客，我们不能失去光彩。\\n\\n心中有爱，有信念在手，有坚定的理解，最美的风景需要用心绽放！\\n\\n通往天堂的道路，拿出你的诚意，创造民族最美的中国梦，创造祖国最美的风景！\",\"timestamp\":1639148723,\"title\":\"BLOOM\"},\"digest\":\"a1cwuC8But7GLUPgHpde__UmWCRRlsSL-unhN4PIRig\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x68103C7932Ed0a74Bd8d4F8442B89355c860182D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"k5Xu2GaraLFdvTB773-ixWF_krEcqhD_M1v0w76-5Js\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"j4APA66EC4RdpOWmCdAzlJQGND2ootRCV74YQGGpb-M\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"bD8GpCLkNKjErqr_Smn3P39937OgCW5ZkvARm6y6LMgt7j3WBB5si8Swv9brGF1aZA_sfAdo7RpCDpuZTSnp8w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x58f37e237d14773e5b182df67d58719b702d35a81d6e1d8f0cca57096e0bc7a311b4d1a5a1a097bae148eca9e053a81a8064f4157ffbd0ada923cc3b725312f91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"k5Xu2GaraLFdvTB773-ixWF_krEcqhD_M1v0w76-5Js\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"j4APA66EC4RdpOWmCdAzlJQGND2ootRCV74YQGGpb-M\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"a1cwuC8But7GLUPgHpde__UmWCRRlsSL-unhN4PIRig\"}"